cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM 

This paper proposes a framework for compressing convolutional neural networks, which is a topic that falls under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also utilizes optimization techniques such as ADMM, which falls under the category of numerical analysis (cs.NE). Finally, the paper evaluates its approach on image classification tasks, which falls under the category of multimedia (cs.MM).
